{"tid":1530273,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[唔跳閘唔買老人飛]水貨客常用慳錢又最安全搭港鐵方法","createTime":"2019-09-02T02:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T06:29:01.000Z","uid":273953,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"608d12c55b570f7c6a20b8d629e0aaeb8dc31a8c","tid":1530273,"uid":273953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:11:49.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人share過，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大家千其唔好學</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買兩張八達通(A卡&amp;B卡)<br />\n用A卡入閘<br />\n出閘時用B卡去客務中心講出唔到閘<br />\n職員會問乘客喺邊個站入閘<br />\n咁乘客就可以噏話係隔離個站(e.g.要旺角出就話自己太子入閘)，咁就會只扣最低收費<br />\n下次搭車就用A卡去客務中心話入唔到閘，職員會幫你void左嗰次入閘記錄，唔會扣錢<br />\n但咁樣void法每張卡只可以做5次，所以玩左4次就唔好再用張卡，入面d錢可以平時買野食野用左佢，或者唔用等退卡<br />\n張卡買左之後3個月內退卡會收手續費，所以放3個月先退卡啦，餘額同按金都會全數退番晒<br />\n<br />\n優點：<br />\n唔駛跳閘<br />\n唔駛買小童/老人飛<br />\n完全唔會俾查飛組捉到你逃票<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<br />\n長期咁做要買好多八達通卡備用<br />\n要花時間排客務中心<br />\n<del>增加港鐵職員工作量</del><br />\n<br />\n再講多次，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家千其唔好學</span></strong>，咁樣查飛組又捉唔到你，港鐵又會賺少好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb43a9734f55a316fcb3f86a80b855308f672c15","tid":1530273,"uid":273953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:13:02.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔郁<br />\n求幫推"},{"pid":"2a02580d8bdbf61a30d5807663ea4ddabe9cb731","tid":1530273,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:13:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ab083cec699b3e991473456fb8eef5afb498259","tid":1530273,"uid":273953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a02580d8bdbf61a30d5807663ea4ddabe9cb731","tid":1530273,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime